  "description": "The aggressive lead. Supersaw at 0.5 spread, filter wide open, zero shimmer, zero chorus — dry, cutting, monophonic. Sub square wave for body. The Guru says: OPENSKY is not only clouds and reverb tails. Strip everything away and the supersaw itself is a weapon. Resonance at the 0.28 SVF shelf for presence without shrillness.",
