    "flock_note": "The Finger played hard and felt the cut — The Tongue identified the 0.28 resonance shelf as 'presence without shrillness', the exact sweet spot.",
    "diagnosis": "Solar Flare reveals OPENSKY's dry lead identity — shimmer zeroed, filter wide open, sub square for body. Proves the engine is not defined by its reverb tail."
